### GraphQL API Test File for Vehicare

@url = http://localhost:5006/graphql

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation RegisterUser($input: RegisterInput!) { register(input: $input) { success user { id email firstName lastName createdAt } error } }",
  "variables": {
    "input": {
      "email": "john.doe@example.com",
      "password": "password123",
      "firstName": "John",
      "lastName": "Doe"
    }
  }
}

### 2. Login user
POST {{url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation LoginUser($input: LoginInput!) { login(input: $input) { success token user { id email firstName lastName lastLoginAt } error } }",
  "variables": {
    "input": {
      "email": "john.doe@example.com",
      "password": "password123"
    }
  }
}

### 3. Get API status (no authentication required)
POST {{url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetStatus { status }"
}

### 4. Get current user (requires authentication - replace with actual token from login)
POST {{url}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_TOKEN

{
  "query": "query GetMe { me { id email firstName lastName createdAt lastLoginAt isActive } }"
}
